  "detailed_description": "<h1>Myth of Empires Xizhou Civilization Pack is now officially released! Welcome to the Era of Multiple Civilizations!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Xizhou Civilization Pack includes a brand-new Xizhou map, a set of Imperial Fall devices, 5 types of functional vehicles, 9 sets of new armor, 16 unique weapons, 2 fine animal saddles, a set of unique building recipes, a construction bench, new consumable, and 3 types of smelting materials. Additionally, the Xizhou Civilization DLC will introduce a new Shah civilization growth system, where players can unlock different development paths based on their skills, gaining unique civilization bonuses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other new features, such as Profession Change, Corps Expertise, Martial Scripture Scrolls, horse grooming, Construction Bureau building, and zipline buildings, will offer even more customization options and fun gameplay experiences for players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/c18342fedf18b69ae5f6139cf84e022f.avif?t=1765253133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras_big/c18342fedf18b69ae5f6139cf84e022f.avif?t=1765253133 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/0d1f3701bde98d0742023909d6d8aa3e.avif?t=1765253133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras_big/0d1f3701bde98d0742023909d6d8aa3e.avif?t=1765253133 width=800 height=1856 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on an Epic Journey – Experience the Rich Tapestry of Diverse Cultures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a vast world forged by the Zhongzhou, Dongzhou, and Xizhou, nature’s wonders awaken as day turns to night. Discover dynamic ecosystems and immerse yourself in unique cultural traditions that promise an unforgettable adventure. Confront the mighty Jiuzhou, Hellas, and Shah civilizations, and choose your own path of development to master your strengths and shape your destiny. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/470e98d496b7a84e419e648f95ad010e.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/470e98d496b7a84e419e648f95ad010e.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/470e98d496b7a84e419e648f95ad010e.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Creativity and Forge Your Empire</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience unparalleled sandbox freedom where diverse civilizations boast unique weapons, armor, and architecture. With over 1,300 crafting recipes at your disposal, create an empire that stands apart and opens up a world of endless possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/62bc4fce56c86321e4e0c62df8fe29f4.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/62bc4fce56c86321e4e0c62df8fe29f4.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/62bc4fce56c86321e4e0c62df8fe29f4.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit NPCs, Tame Wildlife</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subdue and recruit NPCs, horses, animals large and small, and elite Beast Lords. Myth of Empires’ deep taming and breeding systems allow you to cultivate an army of man and beast that will help you with both combat and transportation, and aid you in your journey to becoming emperor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/7c3f92d3e2044335f4e5699d89d3aab8.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/7c3f92d3e2044335f4e5699d89d3aab8.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/7c3f92d3e2044335f4e5699d89d3aab8.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Epic Battles on Land, Air, and Sea</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Myth of Empires features hundreds of different weapons, armor, and siege equipment from multiple civilizations. Construct massive fortresses to defend your territory, or take your armies to the battlefield and immerse yourself in thrilling ancient warfare!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/3e479740144c8ab45f239b9b4c863598.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/3e479740144c8ab45f239b9b4c863598.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/3e479740144c8ab45f239b9b4c863598.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engage in Cross-server Battles </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Establish administrative regions, fight for the position of county magistrate, and compete to expand your territory through Fortress Battles. Craft the perfect guild and utilize your diplomatic prowess to ensure its long-term stability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/99f65ebc9e63468607ce3cc01cdf93f8.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/99f65ebc9e63468607ce3cc01cdf93f8.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/99f65ebc9e63468607ce3cc01cdf93f8.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Civilization Growth Paths – Write Your Own Legend </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 25 unique development paths, leverage a 16-tier Nobility system, and unlock over 100 achievements. Our brand-new profession change system lays the foundation for a truly one-of-a-kind experience. Each civilization brings its own unique strengths, putting the power of choice in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/c0327dff8754ff47715d7b6f110d7d0c.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/c0327dff8754ff47715d7b6f110d7d0c.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/c0327dff8754ff47715d7b6f110d7d0c.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Multiple Gameplay Modes Offering Endless Possibilities </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Myth of Empires supports official servers, custom servers, as well as solo and hosted modes. Creative players are also able to use the game’s robust mod editor to tailor the game to their dream experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/b5483117c3ca0d0e63964860de2826c2.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/b5483117c3ca0d0e63964860de2826c2.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/b5483117c3ca0d0e63964860de2826c2.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on an Epic Journey – Experience the Rich Tapestry of Diverse Cultures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a vast world forged by the Zhongzhou, Dongzhou, and Xizhou, nature’s wonders awaken as day turns to night. Discover dynamic ecosystems and immerse yourself in unique cultural traditions that promise an unforgettable adventure. Confront the mighty Jiuzhou, Hellas, and Shah civilizations, and choose your own path of development to master your strengths and shape your destiny. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/470e98d496b7a84e419e648f95ad010e.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/470e98d496b7a84e419e648f95ad010e.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/470e98d496b7a84e419e648f95ad010e.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Creativity and Forge Your Empire</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience unparalleled sandbox freedom where diverse civilizations boast unique weapons, armor, and architecture. With over 1,300 crafting recipes at your disposal, create an empire that stands apart and opens up a world of endless possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/62bc4fce56c86321e4e0c62df8fe29f4.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/62bc4fce56c86321e4e0c62df8fe29f4.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/62bc4fce56c86321e4e0c62df8fe29f4.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit NPCs, Tame Wildlife</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subdue and recruit NPCs, horses, animals large and small, and elite Beast Lords. Myth of Empires’ deep taming and breeding systems allow you to cultivate an army of man and beast that will help you with both combat and transportation, and aid you in your journey to becoming emperor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/7c3f92d3e2044335f4e5699d89d3aab8.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/7c3f92d3e2044335f4e5699d89d3aab8.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/7c3f92d3e2044335f4e5699d89d3aab8.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Epic Battles on Land, Air, and Sea</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Myth of Empires features hundreds of different weapons, armor, and siege equipment from multiple civilizations. Construct massive fortresses to defend your territory, or take your armies to the battlefield and immerse yourself in thrilling ancient warfare!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/3e479740144c8ab45f239b9b4c863598.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/3e479740144c8ab45f239b9b4c863598.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/3e479740144c8ab45f239b9b4c863598.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engage in Cross-server Battles </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Establish administrative regions, fight for the position of county magistrate, and compete to expand your territory through Fortress Battles. Craft the perfect guild and utilize your diplomatic prowess to ensure its long-term stability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/99f65ebc9e63468607ce3cc01cdf93f8.poster.avif?t=1765253133\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/99f65ebc9e63468607ce3cc01cdf93f8.webm?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371580/extras/99f65ebc9e63468607ce3cc01cdf93f8.mp4?t=1765253133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Civilization Growth Paths – Write Your Own Legend </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 25 unique development paths, leverage a 16-tier Nobility system, and unlock over 100 achievements. Our brand-new profession change system lays the foundation for a truly one-of-a-kind experience. Each civilization brings its own unique strengths, putting the power of choice in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/